00:40:46.319 --> 00:40:49.364
I'm very sorry
for the inconvenience, sir.

460
00:40:49.447 --> 00:40:53.409
Take him home first.
And apologize again!

461
00:40:53.493 --> 00:40:57.497
Be careful with Sandy Claws
when you fetch him! Treat him nicely!

462
00:40:57.580 --> 00:41:01.167
