for doing such a good job!

656
00:59:11.465 --> 00:59:16.470
Whoa! Careful down there.
You almost hit us!

657
00:59:16.553 --> 00:59:20.348
It's OK, Zero. Head higher!

658
00:59:24.644 --> 00:59:27.481
Are you a gamblin' man, Sandy?

659
00:59:27.564 --> 00:59:29.357
Let's play!

660
00:59:32.444 --> 00:59:34.404
My, my!

661
00:59:34.488 --> 00:59:37.324
What have we here?

662
00:59:46.666 --> 00:59:48.919
I'll get you out of here.

663
00:59:50.670 --> 00:59:53.173
Lovely!

664
00:59:53.256 --> 00:59:56.676
Tickle, tickle, tickle.
Tickle, tickle, tickle.

665
01:00:00.680 --> 01:00:05.102
What?! You try
to make a dupe out of me?!

666
01:00:16.863 --> 01:00:19.366
Who's next on my list?

667
01:00:20.534 --> 01:00:23.912
Little Harry and Jordan.
Won't they be surprised?

668
01:00:35.715 --> 01:00:39.761
They're trying to hit us! Zero!

669
01:00:49.771 --> 01:00:52.357
Merry Christmas to all,

670
01:00:52.440 --> 01:00:56.027
and to all a good night!

671
01:01:15.755 --> 01:01:20.218
I knew this Christmas thing
was a bad idea.

672
01:01:20.302 --> 01:01:23.221
I felt it in my gut.

673
01:01:24.264 --> 01:01:26.933
Terrible news, folks!

674
01:01:27.058 --> 01:01:31.062
The worst tragedy of our times!

675
01:01:31.146 --> 01:01:35.400
Jack has been blown to smithereens!

676
01:01:37.110 --> 01:01:40.822
Terrible, terrible news!

677
01:01:43.116 --> 01:01:47.829
Attention. Attention, citizens.
Terrible news.

678
01:01:47.913 --> 01:01:51.666
There's still no sign of Santa Claus.

679
01:01:51.750 --> 01:01:54.461
Although the impostor
has been shot down,

680
01:01:54.544 --> 01:02:00.342
it looks like Christmas will have
